<lyrics>[V1]
 1- nsjtny bhdwʾ ydạk kwntạny
 fạmtzt ṣnʿạaⁿ ʿjybạaⁿ wrwʿẗ wmʿạny
 tẖm nẓrt ạ̹ly bkl ḥb ạlkyạn
 dʿwtny ạ̉nt bạ̹smy wqlt ly ..ạ̉nt ly
 2- ʿly̱ ṣlyb dẖnwby ydạk kẖlṣtạny
 fʿdt ḥrạaⁿ krymạaⁿ tmsẖy mʿy bḥnạn
 tẖm nẓrt ạ̹lyk ạ̹ly̱ jrwḥ ạlydyn
 nqsẖtny ạ̉nt bạ̹smy wqlt ly ..ạ̉nt ly
 3- mḥbh ttsạmy ḥwly wtsby kyạny
 tḥṣrny kl ywm wtgẖmrn zmạny
 ḥty̱ yḥyn ạ̉ntqạly ạ̹ly̱ ạlʿly̱ bạ̉mạn
 tndhny ạ̉nt bạsmy tẖq lạ tkẖf ..ạ̉nt ly</lyrics>
